><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uflynte1.showPublicProfile?language=EN>flynte1</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(2/14/02 12:44:12 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousethebackroomsecretsspoilers.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=9838.topic&index=106>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: re</span><hr size=1> For those saying Aaryonar is harder now I beg to disagree.  Besides the fact the two guards must be fought at the same time he is no harder.  He died in the same amount of time as usual with only a couple of losses due to the guards and low health agros.  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/ucylus.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Cylus</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(2/14/02 12:47:47 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousethebackroomsecretsspoilers.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=9838.topic&index=107>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: re</span><hr size=1> NToV was a joke before and is on it's way to being balanced...wooopty @#%$ doo, let's please find something better to bitch about... <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uhakatri.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Hakatri</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(2/14/02 12:48:57 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousethebackroomsecretsspoilers.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=9838.topic&index=108>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: re</span><hr size=1> He has at least 50% more